description: This skill will ask user 5 questions on the basic knowledge regarding the stories and characters of the online game world of warcraft , and each question answered correctly will score 1 point for the user. There is no prerequisites needed.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, tell wow trivia to start
Alexa, ask wow trivia to start
Alexa, ask wow trivia to start a new game
name: WOWTrivia
shortDescription: This is an Alexa skill that test user on knowledge about online game video game world of warcraft.
